```Today we talked about our progress & a new marketing idea: a Coliquidity widget for partner websites. Tune in to the AMA to learn more!```

```We talked about CryptoWiki - a project that generates different explanations of the same concept depending on the users current knowledge. Basically, it rewrites the articles for each visitor, depending on what he already knows.

Its a great idea for marketing Coliquidity, because a) We need this tool for ourselves, since we have users with very different backgrounds b) People search for information about crypto in Google, and we can rank higher with multiple unique contextual articles.

We are pushing forward with our current marketing strategy (rebrand + partnerships). However, the CryptoWiki idea sounds very promising, so well explore it after the current strategy shows its fruits.```
